# Build System Module
#
# Orchestrates compilation, testing, and packaging for the Simple compiler.
# Provides a unified build interface accessed through the CLI.
#
# Public API:
#   - use app.build.cli_entry.{handle_build}  # Main CLI entry point
#
# Internal Components:
#   - Build orchestration (orchestrator, main)
#   - Bootstrap builds (bootstrap, bootstrap_safe)
#   - Testing (test, coverage)
#   - Quality checks (quality: lint, format, check)
#   - Package management (package)
#   - Build modes (incremental, watch)
#   - Platform-specific (baremetal, cargo)

# All submodules are automatically available through the module system.
# Import them directly: use app.build.cli_entry.{handle_build}

# Re-exported from alloc_checker.spl
export AllocCheckError, alloc_check_error_new
